  &lt;/span&gt;Looking for bodyweight workouts? Freeletics has more than 900 that last anywhere from 10 to 30 minutes. Whether you choose to work out in the kitchen, on the subway, or in your office, you can rely on Freeletics to deliver a great workout for your fitness level. (Free; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/freeletics-bodyweight-workouts/id654810212?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.freeletics.lite&amp;amp;hl=en&quot;&gt;Android&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
