  &lt;/span&gt;The field of calorie-counting apps is heavily saturated, but ShopWell still manages to stand out. The app is all about personalization. Enter in your height, weight, age, and allergies, and then it scores every food you can think of on how healthy it is for you&mdash;the closer to 100, the better. And it even makes individual recommendations for similar, healthier products to eat instead. (Free; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/shopwell-healthy-diet-grocery/id393422300?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.shopwell.shopwellandroid&amp;amp;hl=en&quot;&gt;Android&lt;/a&gt;) &lt;/p&gt;
