  &lt;/span&gt;So you&rsquo;re totally game to try out new recipes, but fiddling with your phone to follow the directions while your hands are sticky is a huge pain. That&rsquo;s where SideChef comes in. The app provides step-by-step voice command instructions. If it&rsquo;s going too fast, you can ask SideChef to repeat directions without ever having to get your phone dirty&mdash;or worse, waterlogged. (Free; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/sidechef-step-by-step-cooking/id905229928?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.sidechef.sidechef&amp;amp;hl=en&quot;&gt;Android&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
