  &lt;/span&gt;We have the best of intentions when it comes to eating healthy, but Rise is the app that really keeps you honest. It pairs you up with a nutritionist, and every day you send them photos of the food you&rsquo;ve eaten. Based on your specific goal (losing weight, gaining strength, feeling more energized), your nutritionist will help you tweak your diet. At $14.99 per week, it&rsquo;s cheaper than IRL appointments with an R.D. (Free with optional in-app purchases; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/rise-nutrition-weight-loss/id794278760?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
