  &lt;/span&gt;Just like its name implies, this app forces you to put your money where your mouth is and show you&rsquo;re not full of hot air when it comes to your weight-loss goals. Users enter into a challenge where they can bet they&rsquo;ll lose either 4 percent of their weight in four weeks or 10 percent of their weight in six months. Progress is monitored by DietBet&rsquo;s referees, and the pot is then split between everyone in your group who makes their goal weight. (Free to download, $25-$25 per bet; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dietbet-lose-weight.-make/id532353287?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.dietbet.app&amp;amp;hl=en&quot;&gt;Android&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
