  &lt;/span&gt;Dieting can be so complex. Don&rsquo;t have time to check your macros (or don&rsquo;t know what those are)? Time to download Noom Coach. Unlike other calorie-counting apps, Noom uses the stoplight approach (green is good, red is not so great) to label healthy food. And you can join in on challenges with other Noomers to get even more motivated to meet your health goals. (Free with optional in-app purchases; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/noom-coach-weight-loss/id634598719?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wsl.noom&amp;amp;hl=en&quot;&gt;Android&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
