  &lt;/span&gt;Ah, the drunk uncle of meditation apps&mdash;it wants the best for you, but you know it will tell it like it f*cking is. Strangely enough, cussing and calm really do make a good combination. If anything, H*nest Meditation is bringing calm to the common (wo)man, and we&rsquo;re damn grateful for that. Just make sure to wear your headphones. ($1.99; &lt;a href=&quot;https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/h*nest-meditation/id1059195733?mt=8&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
