      &lt;/section&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Methodology: We asked a number of questions to determine if each app we tested should appear on our list. Is it highly rated? Does it offer something unique? It is user-friendly? Is it reliable and not buggy? Does it drain a smartphone&rsquo;s battery? Can it continue to grow and innovate? Apps that scored well on all criteria ended up the final list. Do you think we missed an app? Send a message to &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:tips@greatist.com&quot;&gt;tips@greatist.com&lt;/a&gt;, and we&rsquo;ll consider it for next year&rsquo;s ranking. &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; ",
